## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

- Python 3.11+
- MCP Mesh SDK
- FastMCP

### Installation

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

{{ if .AuthBearer }}### Authentication

The producer advertises bearer authentication. Set your token via:

```bash
export {{ .AuthEnvVar }}=<your-bearer-token>
```
{{ end }}### Running the Agent

```bash
meshctl start main.py
```

The agent will start on port {{ .Port }} by default (override with `MCP_MESH_HTTP_PORT`).

